{"tid":611474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[優質之選]加拿大狗糧標明「不含支那成分」　引來華人抵制","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T14:41:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":623,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"a16fc8222e98b22f04702b39ef2647a8364bee07","tid":611474,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180331/s00005/1522472152155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180331%2Fs00005%2F1522472152155&d=4%2BrRIQTk%2BJ4g0iBcleXrgQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=562cf5bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180331%2Fs00005%2F1522472152155&h=51a77e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180331/s00005/1522472152155</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180331/s00005/c7fea6c6e607dc7ad3412bdb6515f5c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180331%2Fs00005%2Fc7fea6c6e607dc7ad3412bdb6515f5c3.jpg&h=b9667baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大近日一個寵物糧食品牌因在產品包裝上標註「不含中國成分」（NO ingredients from China），引起當地不少華人熱議，批評公司分化社會，令消費者對中國產品有偏見。<br />\n<br />\n「列治文新聞」（Richmond News）網站當地時間周三（28日）報道，華人杜小姐在超市購買Honest Kitchen品牌的狗糧，回家後卻發現包裝上寫有「不含中國成分」（NO ingredients from China），表示沒有使用任何來自中國的原料。她感到被冒犯，不明白為何超市會出現這種產品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜小姐表示，這類宣傳手法會分化當地社區，助長人們對中國產品產生偏見、購買不含中國原料的貨品。她認為這種取態不健康。<br />\n<br />\n對於狗糧上的標註，該超市的職員亦感到奇怪，認為本意可能是強調產品不含任何來自其他國家的原料，但不明白為何只提及中國，估計可能與部分顧客認為中國食品質素較差有關。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>涉事寵物糧食公司Honest Kitchen回應稱，有關包裝是由於「品牌的食品安全控制」，並非針對單一國家或國民，稱店內同樣有中國顧客，他們亦不希望使用內含中國原料的產品。<br />\n<br />\n公司又表示，2007年美國曾有不少寵物死亡，其後大規模回收寵物糧食，發現大部分問題糧食含有來自中國的原料，當中有用於製作膠餐具的化學物質。公司強調有關包裝只是表達公司對旗下品牌的食品安全有嚴格控制。</strong><br />\n<br />\n然而，許多當地華人皆表示不能接受該公司的做法，聲言會抵制該公司的所有品牌和門市。<br />\n<br />\n（列治文新聞/環球網）"},{"pid":"ea2eecb7cb57a763403dc478c16dc12ec08479a7","tid":611474,"uid":170772,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"攞黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fbf0e86cc608706ac9dcb2f1107a1da04cdf99","tid":611474,"uid":148355,"like":102,"dislike":2,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:03:48.000Z","msg":"免費宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58018c604d33c2845af2d97596d98b3a0673a8ab","tid":611474,"uid":51920,"like":154,"dislike":7,"score":147,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"支那人一路屌一路瘋搶"},{"pid":"92af42a4911a3dd26bf8a2efbac91b4cd1e751ab","tid":611474,"uid":122,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"屌完再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84967c91ff3d3109b724ffa6043319ce7b058745","tid":611474,"uid":63950,"like":176,"dislike":2,"score":174,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7740f8dc5f232a9f9b64456e4617500a3e3f002f","tid":611474,"uid":169918,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"跟住買得最多係支那人"},{"pid":"888f2975d883654e536812e0592dd80e90e43dad","tid":611474,"uid":44454,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"講真，狗糧冇中國成份真係講唔過去嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230d675324997b58eb4a0877888ea3bbef30b818","tid":611474,"uid":129664,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"咁咪買啲含支那成份既狗糧囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eee6c4a73c4e58cd563dc0efd3b9d664fef4226","tid":611474,"uid":60545,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12